name: note_for_programmers_this_ent
label: Note for programmers: This entire section should only be displayed if "plutonic" or "volcanic" is selected for Rock Type from the Petrology Basics page.

name: note_for_programmers_strabosp
label: Note for programmers: StraboSpot will need to calculate normalized values from the total combined values from the Q, A, P fields. The normalized value for each should be displayed next to the entry field for each Q, A, P entry field. The normalized value for Q = Q/(Q+A+P), etc.
